description: [Розширений пошук] Verify that the clubs can be sorted alphabetically

parameters.name: arg1
parameters.value:
SELECT DISTINCT c.name
FROM clubs as c
INNER JOIN locations as l ON c.id=l.club_id
INNER JOIN cities as ct ON l.city_id=ct.id
WHERE ct.name = 'Київ'
ORDER BY c.name DESC;
